### 1. Home - Check all routes
GET http://localhost:5000/

###

### 2. Health check (Ollama + server status)
GET http://localhost:5000/health

###

### 3. First aid search (English)
GET http://localhost:5000/firstaid?q=choking&lang=en

###

### 4. First aid search (Hindi)
GET http://localhost:5000/firstaid?q=choking&lang=hi

###

### 5. Get shelters by city
GET http://localhost:5000/shelters?city=Solapur

###

### 6. Evacuation instructions (English)
GET http://localhost:5000/evacuation?type=flood&lang=en

###

### 7. Evacuation instructions (Hindi)
GET http://localhost:5000/evacuation?type=flood&lang=hi

###

### 8. Main emergency query (DB + AI fallback)
POST http://localhost:5000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "someone is choking",
  "mode": "medical",
  "lang": "en",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

###

### 9. Main emergency query (flood mode)
POST http://localhost:5000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "flood evacuation",
  "mode": "flood",
  "lang": "en",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

###

### 10. Direct AI query only (bypass DB)
POST http://localhost:5000/ai
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "how to treat a burn injury",
  "mode": "medical"
}

###

### 13. Translate English to Hindi
POST http://localhost:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Apply pressure to the wound immediately",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "hi"
}

###

### 14. Translate English to Malayalam
POST http://localhost:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Move to higher ground immediately",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "ml"
}

###

### 15. Translate English to Marathi
POST http://localhost:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Call emergency services immediately",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "mr"
}

###

### 16. Ask with auto-translation (query in Hindi, response in Hindi)
POST http://localhost:5000/ask_translated
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "कोई दम घुट रहा है",
  "mode": "medical",
  "lang": "hi",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

###

### 17. Ask with auto-translation (English query, Malayalam response)
POST http://localhost:5000/ask_translated
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "someone is choking",
  "mode": "medical",
  "lang": "ml",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

###

### Question NOT in database — Ollama handles it
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "what to do during a tsunami",
  "mode": "general",
  "lang": "en",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

