### Translate English to Kannada
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Apply pressure to stop the bleeding.",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "kn"
}

### Ask in Kannada
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/ask_translated
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "ರಕ್ತಸ್ರಾವ ನಿಲ್ಲಿಸುವುದು ಹೇಗೆ",
  "mode": "medical",
  "lang": "kn",
  "city": "Solapur"
}

### Should use hardcoded — instant and accurate
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "choking",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "ta"
}

### Should use hardcoded partial match
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Go to hospital immediately",
  "from": "en",
  "to": "kn"
}